reviews.text: The worst Korean restaurant in hk. Waited for long time when we were the only table there, and decided to leave and the waitress still wanted to charge us, so We waited longer and they just bought us lousy dishes. Black bean noodle was just instant noodle which took them 20mins to cook. The pork belly rice was a disaster, overcooked, burned, extremely dry, very salty. We ended up leaving the food and wasted the lunch money.

味道不錯 但地方太窄
